# CODEOWNERS for ProjectMeats
# This file defines who should review PRs for different parts of the codebase
# 
# Each line is a file pattern followed by one or more owners.
# These owners will be automatically requested for review when someone 
# opens a pull request that modifies files matching the pattern.
#
# More details: https://docs.github.com/en/repositories/managing-your-repositorys-settings-and-features/customizing-your-repository/about-code-owners

# Default owners for everything in the repo
# This is a catch-all - specific patterns below override this
